12/16/2025,Ad progression - customized funnels based on value propsitions,"Currently, this is very little connection between the marketing ad that a user clicks on and the conversion funnel. We are testing personalized funnels that dynamically change based on the message of the marketing ad a user clicks on (e.g.; users clicking on a health ad will go through a health-themed conversion funnel). ",Yes,"Conversion Comms Squad, Growth Alliance",Harneet Singh Alvaro Magalhaes Aleksandr Shalaev,"Statsig 
JIRA (HF) 
JIRA (Factor) 
Slide deck",,,was on agenda last week and didn't get to them

12/16/2025,WMS 2.0 Single Pick -> Multi drop Replenishment,We built a new inventory replenishment approach for the Netherlands production facilaiity to optimize getting stock to our kitting lines as quickly as possible in our best performing warehouse in the world,Yes,SCM Inventory Management,Adrian Southwart Jasper van Leeuwen,,1,,has an external visitor in this office this week and pre-arranged to demo this week

12/16/2025,Indirect Procurement Integration,"We will be talking about the indirect procurement integration between Workday Procurement and Oracle Finance, which helped roll out Workday procurement across HelloFresh.",Yes,"SCM Inventory Management
",Santhosh Raju / Trishul Venkata Reddy,,2,,

12/16/2025,New Cooking Experince on the App ,,,"Growth Alliance, Active Journey Alliance ",Wladimir Gaus Srishti Shah,,3,,

12/16/2025,AI Automated accessibility Scanner,"Our new AI scanner for accessibility integrated with github workflow runs daily, scans the react native code base for WCAG 2.2 AA violations. Generates report based on ownership showing violations by file, priority, team",Yes,Consumer Acceleration,"Teja Chirala ,Meggie Bouchard","Report

",,,could be swapped with Social Recipe Grader for variety in topics (Accessibility instead of social recipe grader)

12/16/2025,Social Recipe Grader,"We've automated the labeling of recipes imported from social media. This demo showcases the review tool we created to verify that the data meets our quality standards. The Recipe Grader is a web application used by the Inspire Squad product team to evaluate the accuracy of recipes extracted and saved by users in their cookbook. The tool provides an intuitive interface that enables side-by-side comparison of three evaluation sources: user ratings, human evaluations, and AI-generated evaluations, each with corresponding quality scores to assess extraction correctness.",Yes,Customer Engagement / Inspire,Wilton Garcia / Emmanuel Kasulani,,4,,"follow up to the social media upload tool already demo'd. if too similar, could be swapped for AI Accessibility tool"

12/16/2025,Enhanced Delivery Options Modal in the Logistics Configurator,"The introduction of fast delivery services (BOLT/NDD) has significantly increased the complexity and volume of delivery options within the Logistics Configurator, making the old UI cumbersome to use (ie. a single UK region went from 63 to 198 options). To solve this, a new Enhanced Delivery Options Modal has been developed, allowing users to manage this complexity more efficiently by customizing visible attributes and applying filters, thereby streamlining the tasks of adding and removing delivery options across regions.",Planned Go Live for W50,SCM Logistics - Delivery Network,Iria Maron Lopez Fatih Ercik Ruth Bochere Ogendi,,5,,

12/16/2025,CLV for Actives - box count prediction model,"We launched the model globally, and integrated it in Statsig, to enable faster decisions and long term visibility in A/B testings. ",Yes,Growth Alliance - Customer Value Forecasting Squad,Jessica Tyler Shriram Rangarajan Yiqing Cai,Git,6,,

12/16/2025,Embedded Message Campaigns in Iterable,"The goal of this demo is to show how to create embedded message campaigns in Iterable, featuring rapid campaign setup, dynamic audience selection, and carousel functionality for managing multiple campaigns.",Yes,Growth Alliance - CRM Engine,"Bruno Oliveira, Zeinab Khosravinia",,,,

12/16/2025,Project DISH: Debox Ingredient Staging Harmonization,WMS directed work order picking and staging to improve inventory accuracy in the storage chambers and work order picking efficiency,Yes,SCM Inventory Management,Yuting Tian Amit Joshi,,,,
